{"tid":283371,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬體會後衛因為同女友去度假被西班牙警方拘捕","createTime":"2017-06-14T06:22:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T06:44:09.000Z","uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60ae2fa035378ccc7515c3dc70e2407a8be3fc18","tid":283371,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T06:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170614/large/1497405801_6dbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170614%2Flarge%2F1497405801_6dbe.jpg&h=b5182b44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬德里體育會的法國後衛盧卡斯靴南迪斯由於違返要與前女友保持500米距離的禁制令，周二再被警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n21歲的盧卡斯靴南迪斯，今年2月因為毆打女友Amelia Lorente被捕，最後避過了牢獄之災，但就被判31日社會服務令以及六個月內不得接近Amelia六個月，至少要與Amelia保持500米距離。然而據西班牙電台《Onda Cero》報道，盧卡斯最近與Amelia復合，更一起到巴哈馬度假，不過就違反了禁制令，因此度假完畢返回西班牙便遭到拘捕，被扣留在馬德里的Moratalaz警局，而盧卡斯會在周三上庭。"},{"pid":"a379f7a9517ffefec3c8baac6a47349acf7ddb67","tid":283371,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T06:24:26.000Z","msg":"好心復合左就取消禁制令啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5290cd6657259e182c0072f63f874e636744cb18","tid":283371,"uid":1082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T06:28:06.000Z","msg":"我仲以為係唔去踢波比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34baf849cae9e10fceb135e962711ab8241176d","tid":283371,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T06:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我仲以為係唔去踢波比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n心諗咁樣都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.